title: Ranked ,  token
body: I played Warwick In Ranked , I got a -S and i dident got anny token , he is already lvl 6 and i need 3 tokens to lvl 7 , why dident i get one?

replies.body: To get those mastery 7 tokens you need to get an S or S+. You were really close though, you may just need more vision or creep score!
Unfortunately, an S- rank does not count for a mastery 7 token. To get a Mastery 7 token, you need to get either an S or S+ rank.
